      "text": "<p><code>container</code> class should have a <code>grid-template-columns</code> property that is set to repeat 3 columns with the width of <code>1fr</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(\n  code.match(\n    /.container\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-columns\\s*?:\\s*?repeat\\s*?\\(\\s*?3\\s*?,\\s*?1fr\\s*?\\)\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\n  )\n);"
